OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny early
OL,6,Fevening showers soon dying away,
OL,7,Fleaving clearing skies, with winds
OL,8,Feasing. This will allow temperatures
OL,9,Fto fall with the chance of ground
OL,10,Ffrost developing in prone rural spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA dry, sunny and chilly start.
OL,13,FCloud bubbling up during the morning
OL,14,Fbut still with sunny spells. Cloud
OL,15,Fthen thickening through the afternoon,
OL,16,Fwith isolated showers possible later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
