OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FOften
OL,6,Fcloudy on Monday with showers
OL,7,Fspreading inland from coastal areas.
OL,8,FDrier on Tuesday and Wednesday with
OL,9,Fsunny spells. Becoming breezy, feeling
OL,10,Fcool especially on coasts. Chilly
OL,11,Fovernight.
